Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近水源了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处在那尤古和萨古的夹缝之中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题 宴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 这些花是我们最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用这个去就查古穆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护查古穆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药草师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些花对我们也有效吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要稍微施加一点咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕无论是谁都能触碰到那尤古的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这花也分给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会让你希望白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是想真么拜托你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要保护好查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感激
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吃了就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去查古穆去的那尤古
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经看不见刚才的食卵者了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是西沽花的效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定没这么快起效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是要相信药草师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在追上王子是首要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从占星师那里到底得到了什么样的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修加大人说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到紧要关头的时候忘记精灵的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之保护王子是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上来说是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就赌他这个判断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算卵被孵化了 但查古穆死了的话就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算止血了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是生物没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像不出是这个世界上的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你收到传讯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后巴尔沙他们朝着萨南去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不亏是托卢卡师所教授的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个这是什么 这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃了西沽花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以花为触媒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也能感触到那尤古的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个花还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 全都给了巴尔沙他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的年龄的话还有一次机会能看到精灵的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是最后一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托卢卡师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在要追上王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明之前不会被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只熊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉伦加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕那是尤佳罗伊穆的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想到了查古穆以外的精灵守护人但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那样的被淘汰掉就是大自然的哲理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 查古穆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看来黎明之前这段时间也不是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快走吧 占星师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅 也带上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 让他一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你骑马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议 完全不觉得冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是萨南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要生下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用短枪的 你先去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法拦住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寸 射这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那尤古这里是水里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这里在那尤古是水里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先到山崖上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到见王子吗 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟子看得见我看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所了解的世界只是这个世界的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只有万分之一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不能杀死拉伦加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要出生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我不被拉伦加撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就出不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 这样我不知道该怎么办才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅 我先去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头领 箭已经没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右也没有多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的8人武士在这种情况下战斗了三天三夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使油没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了那个药草师我们可以和那尤古之物厮杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算豁出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这一把剑也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像头领说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不可能做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用短枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带王子离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让王子逃走是首要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵想留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天不在这里孵化的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵就会死在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵想要在这里孵化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 用短枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 我也还想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的身体被命运所左右
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法做到牺牲大家而活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能牺牲萨古百万百姓的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做只有我能够做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子 不要管我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棠鞑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是去了那尤古
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才师傅教了我取出精灵之卵的咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先要把查古穆代到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 占星师说200年前也用了同样的办法 差一点就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不用担心 查古穆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托卢卡师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有我们能做的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静的等待黎明的到来并祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆 拜托了 快动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少只
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托卢卡师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来在很很多的拉伦加在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 跟上用短枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 萨古的太阳升起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话那尤古和萨古会完全分离的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 把手借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样慢慢的把收伸进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样接触到卵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是卵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全的生下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去 想活下去的心愿实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棠鞑 巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔沙 给让看看卵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个不来的话刚生下来的卵会立刻死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是纳吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没注意到就飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 会注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查古穆 该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把卵扔上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉就会叼走卵的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样就可以护送王子回宫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:23:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 和命运的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.59,0:24:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.82,0:24:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把卵托付给纳吉的查古穆和巴尔沙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.84,0:24:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成一切归来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待他们的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.37,0:24:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终回 启程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.27,0:24:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会忘记 你的一切


